conditioned spaces for hot summers, knowledgeable animal handlers, offering pet care. Their services offers peace of mind for busy North Carolina pet parents. conveniently located in the heart of Fayetteville. Contact Westover Park today to schedule your dog's visit\",\"slug\":\"westover-park\",\"address\":\"267 Bonanza Dr\",\"street\":\"267 Bonanza Dr\",\"city\":\"Fayetteville\",\"state\":\"NC\",\"zipCode\":\"28303\",\"full_address\":\"267 Bonanza Dr, Fayetteville, NC 28303, USA\",\"latitude\":35.0825692,\"longitude\":-78.98978749999999,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJI9fjksJqq4kRSXVdlUUYAdE\",\"phone\":\"(910) 433-1088\",\"rating\":4.2,\"reviewCount\":289,\"userRatingsTotal\":289,\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"unknown\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"8:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"8:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"8:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"8:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"8:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"8:30 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"2:00 – 5:00 PM\"},\"faqs\":[],\"amenities\":{},\"photos\":[{\"url\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/westover-park/westover-park-1.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"},{\"url\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/westover-park/westover-park-2.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"}],\"photo\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/westover-park/westover-park-1.jpg\",\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"}],\"cityName\":\"Fayetteville\",\"insightCards\":\"$undefined\",\"topAmenities\":[],\"insightIntro\":\"$undefined\"}]}]}]\n34:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-comparison\",\"className\":\"city-comparison-section\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L41\",null,{\"parks\":\"$33:props:children:props:children:props:parks\",\"cityName\":\"Fayetteville\"}]}]}]\n35:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"park-collections\",\"className\":\"park-collections-section